Set Up 

- In client/js/scopusSearch you have to add your Scopus API Key, Look for "Enter Your API KEY here".

- In server/js/server.js you have to add your Scopus API Key, Look for "Enter Your API KEY here".

Starting server

You need Nodejs installed on a linux machine.

go to server/js in a console and type "node server.js

The client can be deployed on any apache server or run locally
